---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Eric Alex | Tailwebs Case Study">
  <main class="case-study-page">
    
    <section class="project-hero">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="project-category">Business Development & SaaS Product</p>
        <h1 class="project-title">Tailwebs Technology</h1>
        <p class="project-tagline">Driving agency revenue while simultaneously launching an internal AR SaaS product from scratch.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="meta-section">
      <div class="meta-grid">
        <div class="meta-item">
          <h3>Role</h3>
          <p>Business Development Executive</p>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-item">
          <h3>Timeline</h3>
          <p>Jun. 2024 – Present</p>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-item">
          <h3>Location</h3>
          <p>Bangalore, Karnataka</p>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-item">
          <h3>Focus</h3>
          <p>Sales Ops & GTM Strategy</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>The Journey</h2>
        <p>
          Tailwebs was my first step into the corporate world. I joined as a Business Development Executive at this premier software development firm. 
          My time here has been defined by a dual focus: mastering the sales engine for the core agency business and executing a zero-to-one launch for <strong>ShopAR</strong>, our internal SaaS product.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>Building the Sales Engine</h2>
        <p>
          My first objective was to professionalize our sales operations. I started by mastering <strong>HubSpot</strong>, taking full ownership of CRM management, lead tracking, and follow-up loops.
        </p>
        <p>
          From there, I scaled our outreach using automation tools like <strong>Dripify</strong> (LinkedIn) and <strong>Apollo.io</strong> (Email). I transitioned from simply executing tasks to owning entire campaigns—tracking metrics, planning roadmaps, and eventually taking charge of campaign ideation and content generation alongside the CMO.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bullet-grid">
          <div class="bullet-card">
            <h3>Campaign Ops</h3>
            <p>Executed outbound campaigns; analyzed performance data to optimize targeting, cadence, and messaging.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bullet-card">
            <h3>CRM Management</h3>
            <p>Managed workflows in Zoho and HubSpot to streamline the pipeline and prevent lead leakage.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bullet-card">
            <h3>A/B Testing</h3>
            <p>Created test variations for cold email subject lines and copy, significantly improving open and reply rates.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block highlighted-block">
        <h2>Launching ShopAR</h2>
        <p class="block-intro">
          ShopAR is our internal SaaS allowing retailers to visualize products in AR. I led the Go-To-Market strategy, balancing marketing, content, and sales.
        </p>
        
        <ul class="detailed-list">
          <li>
            <strong>Multi-Channel Sales Testing:</strong> We experimented with 4 distinct channels: Email, Cold Calling, Ads, and Door-to-Door. I personally spent 4 weeks on the ground doing <strong>Door-to-Door sales</strong> to understand customer objections firsthand.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Pivot to Ads:</strong> After analyzing results, we identified that Ads provided the best ROI. I shifted focus to support the ad strategy while managing the onboarding for all incoming users.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Product Feedback Loop:</strong> Acting as the bridge between users and the tech team, I ran structured feedback loops to refine features and improve the product based on real-world usage.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Content & Messaging:</strong> I was responsible for all product content—website copy, in-app messaging, email sequences, and notification strategies.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>Visuals & Process</h2>
        <div class="visuals-grid">
          
          <div class="visual-item">
            <div class="image-frame">
              <img src="/assets/tailwebs-1.png" alt="" />
            </div>
            <p class="caption">CRM & Pipeline Management</p>
          </div>

          <div class="visual-item">
            <div class="image-frame">
              <img src="/assets/tailwebs-2.png" alt="" />
            </div>
            <p class="caption">ShopAR Marketing Campaigns</p>
          </div>

          <div class="visual-item">
            <div class="image-frame">
              <img src="/assets/tailwebs-3.png" alt="" />
            </div>
            <p class="caption">Outreach Analytics</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>Tools & Tech Stack</h2>
        <div class="tech-tags">
          <span>HubSpot</span>
          <span>Zoho CRM</span>
          <span>Apollo.io</span>
          <span>Dripify</span>
          <span>Mixpanel</span>
          <span>Google Analytics 4</span>
          <span>LinkedIn Sales Nav</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <div class="project-footer">
      <a href="/work" class="back-link">&larr; Back to Work</a>
    </div>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* CONSISTENT STYLING (Same as Formi.astro) */
  
  .case-study-page {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px; 
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2.5rem 4rem 2.5rem;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .project-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }
  
  .project-category {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #FF4444; 
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .project-title {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .project-tagline {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
    line-height: 1.4;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  /* METADATA GRID */
  .meta-section {
    padding: 2rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .meta-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .meta-item h3 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .meta-item p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* CONTENT SECTIONS */
  .content-section {
    padding-top: 4rem;
  }

  .content-block {
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .content-block h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .content-block p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  /* BULLET GRID CARDS */
  .bullet-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .bullet-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.031);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .bullet-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .bullet-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
  }

  /* HIGHLIGHTED BLOCK */
  .highlighted-block {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); 
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .detailed-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .detailed-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
  }

  .detailed-list li::before {
    content: "•";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #FF4444; 
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2rem;
  }

  .detailed-list strong {
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  /* VISUALS GRID */
  .visuals-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .visual-item {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .image-frame {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16/10;
    background-color: #222;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .image-frame:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .image-frame img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .caption {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
  }

  /* TECH TAGS */
  .tech-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .tech-tags span {
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  .project-footer {
    margin-top: 6rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .back-link {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: #FF4444;
  }

  /* MOBILE STYLES */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .project-hero {
      padding: 6rem 0 3rem 0;
    }
    .project-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    .project-tagline {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    .meta-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; 
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .bullet-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .visuals-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .highlighted-block {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>